select `project_types`.*, `mentors_project_types`.`mentor_id` as `pivot_mentor_id`, `mentors_project_types`.`project_type_id` as `pivot_project_type_id` from `project_types` inner join `mentors_project_types` on `project_types`.`id` = `mentors_project_types`.`project_type_id` where `mentors_project_types`.`mentor_id` = 127

select * from `students` where `season_id` = 19 and (not exists (select * from `mentors` inner join `mentors_students` on `mentors`.`id` = `mentors_students`.`mentor_id` where `students`.`id` = `mentors_students`.`student_id`) or exists (select * from `mentors` inner join `mentors_students` on `mentors`.`id` = `mentors_students`.`mentor_id` where `students`.`id` = `mentors_students`.`student_id` and `mentor_id` = 127)) and `hours` not in (3, 2, 4) and (not exists (select * from `project_types` inner join `students_project_types` on `project_types`.`id` = `students_project_types`.`project_type_id` where `students`.`id` = `students_project_types`.`student_id`) or exists (select * from `project_types` inner join `students_project_types` on `project_types`.`id` = `students_project_types`.`project_type_id` where `students`.`id` = `students_project_types`.`student_id` and `type` not in (1, 'Социален проект - осъществяване на общественополезна инициатива', '')))

select `mentors`.*, `mentors_students`.`student_id` as `pivot_student_id`, `mentors_students`.`mentor_id` as `pivot_mentor_id` from `mentors` inner join `mentors_students` on `mentors`.`id` = `mentors_students`.`mentor_id` where `mentors_students`.`student_id` in (101, 103, 109)

select `project_types`.*, `students_project_types`.`student_id` as `pivot_student_id`, `students_project_types`.`project_type_id` as `pivot_project_type_id` from `project_types` inner join `students_project_types` on `project_types`.`id` = `students_project_types`.`project_type_id` where `students_project_types`.`student_id` in (101, 103, 109)
